Ext.data.JsonP['Terminal_Class']({"guide":"<?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"UTF-8\" ?>\n<!DOCTYPE html PUBLIC \"-//W3C//DTD XHTML 1.0 Transitional//EN\"\n        \"http://www.w3.org/TR/xhtml1/DTD/xhtml1-transitional.dtd\">\n<html xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\">\n<head>\n    <title>Terminal Class</title>\n\n    <meta http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n    <meta content=\"Scroll EclipseHelp Exporter\" name=\"generator\">\n\n    <link type=\"text/css\" rel=\"stylesheet\">\n    <link type=\"text/css\" rel=\"stylesheet\">\n    <link type=\"text/css\" rel=\"stylesheet\" media=\"print\">\n</link></link></link></meta></meta></head>\n<body>\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <div class=\"header\"/>\n\n        <div id=\"src-30083247\" class=\"content\">\n                        <h1>Terminal Class</h1>\n    <p>The Terminal class contains methods and properties for interacting with the Terminal window inside Studio    </p>\n    <div class=\"section section-2 \" id=\"src-30083247_TerminalClass-Usage\">\n        <h2 class=\"heading \"><span>Usage</span></h2>\n    <p>Examples of how you might interact with methods of the Terminal class.    </p>\n    <div class=\"section section-3 \" id=\"src-30083247_safe-id-VGVybWluYWxDbGFzcy1TdGF0aWM6\">\n        <h3 class=\"heading \"><span>Static:</span></h3>\n    <div class=\"confbox programlisting defaultnew syntaxhighlighter scroll-html-formatted-code\">\n                <div xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\" class=\"defaultnew syntaxhighlighter scroll-html-formatted-code\">\n<div class=\"line\"><code class=\"plain\">require </code><code class=\"string\">&apos;ruble/terminal&apos;</code></div>\n<div class=\"line\"><code class=\"plain\">Ruble::Terminal.open(</code><code class=\"string\">&quot;cap -v #{target}&quot;</code><code class=\"plain\">, ENV[</code><code class=\"string\">&apos;TM_PROJECT_DIRECTORY&apos;</code><code class=\"plain\">])</code></div>\n</div>\n    </div>\n    </div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"section section-2 \" id=\"src-30083247_TerminalClass-TerminalMethods\">\n        <h2 class=\"heading \"><span>Terminal Methods</span></h2>\n    <p>Terminal objects have the following static method:    </p>\n    <div class=\"tablewrap\">\n        <table class=\"confluenceTable\">\n        <thead class=\" \">    <tr>\n            <td class=\"confluenceTh\" rowspan=\"1\" colspan=\"1\">\n        <p>Property    </p>\n            </td>\n                <td class=\"confluenceTh\" rowspan=\"1\" colspan=\"1\">\n        <p>Description    </p>\n            </td>\n        </tr>\n</thead><tfoot class=\" \"/><tbody class=\" \">    <tr>\n            <td class=\"confluenceTd\" rowspan=\"1\" colspan=\"1\">\n        <p><tt class=\" \">open(command, working directory)</tt>    </p>\n            </td>\n                <td class=\"confluenceTd\" rowspan=\"1\" colspan=\"1\">\n        <p>The command to execute, and the working directory in which the execute it. The working directory is optional    </p>\n            </td>\n        </tr>\n</tbody>        </table>\n            </div>\n    </div>\n        </div><a id=\"editButton\" href=\"https://wiki.appcelerator.org/pages/editpage.action?pageId=30083247\"><span>Edit</span></a>\n    \n        \n    </div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","title":"Terminal Class"});